WEBVTT

00:07:28.878 --> 00:07:33.852
Because my nine-year-old son
had to educate his teacher

00:07:33.876 --> 00:07:35.367
about his history,

00:07:35.391 --> 00:07:38.441
had to educate his teacher
about his own humanity.

00:07:38.465 --> 00:07:40.134
He's nine years old.

00:07:40.784 --> 00:07:44.001
He should be thinking about
basketball or soccer

00:07:44.025 --> 00:07:46.496
or the latest movie.

00:07:46.520 --> 00:07:50.687
He should not be thinking about
having to take the responsibility

00:07:50.711 --> 00:07:53.074
of educating his teacher,

00:07:53.098 --> 00:07:56.161
his students,

00:07:56.185 --> 00:07:58.652
about himself, about his history.

00:07:58.676 --> 00:08:00.303
That was a burden that I carried.